text: haey satvapahn muoychamnuon ach doekachonhchoun ban(dauchchea satv audth cheadaem) ning muoychamnuon tiet min ach doekachonhchoun ban te(dauch chea ppe chiem) . chaur puok anak briphok ampi avei del a l laoh ban bratan leaphosakkar mk aoy puok anak choh . haey chaur puok anak kom tam meakra robsa shai t n aoy saoh . pitabrakd nasa vea kuchea sa trauv yeang pitabrakd champoh puok anak
